        </p>

        <form onsubmit="handleSearch(event)" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto relative group mt-14">
        <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-8 flex items-center text-[#5f6368] dark:text-[#9aa0a6]">
            <i data-lucide="search" width="28" height="28" stroke-width="2"></i>
